OL,5, Campaigning Australian journalist and  
OL,6, filmmaker John Pilger has died aged 84,
OL,7, his family has announced.              
OL,9,FA statement by his relatives on X said 
OL,10,Fhe died in London on Saturday.         
OL,12,FThey described Pilger as "simply the   
OL,13,Fmost amazing and loved dad, grandad and
OL,14,Fpartner".                              
OL,16,FHe was a vocal and sometimes           
OL,17,Fcontroversial critic of Western foreign
OL,18,Fpolicy. He was also outspoken over the 
OL,19,Ftreatment of Indigenous Australians.   
